STATE of Iowa, Appellee,
v.
John Walter MULDER, Appellant. No. 75 / 16-0824 Supreme Court of Iowa. Filed April 27, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

A juvenile offender appeals from resentence by the district court to life imprisonment with parole after forty-two years. DECISION OF COURT OF APPEALS VACATED; DISTRICT COURT JUDGMENT REVERSED AND REMANDED.

VACATED. REVERSED. REMANDED.
